case1: python qxyz2eps.py 
case2: python qxyz2eps.py dump.qxyz.txt 
if no file argument, default file name will be dump.qxyz.txt
copy atom_group.py_example to atom_group.py and modify it

groups define the dipole calculation groups
temperature is obviuse
dt: recording steps 20 and the time_step for MD

groups = [[1, 44],[44,88],[88, 132], [132, 176], [176, 220],[220, 264], [264, 314],[314,364],[364,414],[414,464],[464,514],[514,564]]
temperature = 600.0
dt = 0.2e-15 *20
